description:
Danny is joined by Hannah Brown (host of the Brown-Eyed Jewnicorn podcast) to recap this week's Real Housewives of New York. They discuss Sonja's art friend and his studio/Petsmart, plus the return of Mario, the movie Burlesque, Barb's wrap dresses, and so much more. They also deep-dive into Cindy Barshop.


*To support this podcast & access bonus eps, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
